Requirements:
Digital Mars D2 Compiler
D Forms Library tool (dfl.exe)
UPX
rcc (from Digital Mars)

For debug build:
run build.bat
tspion.exe and hook.dll will appear in the current directory

For release build:
run build_release.bat
tspion.exe and hook.dll
tspion.exe and hook.dll will appear in the build directory

For creating a packed launcher:
first make sure you have done a release build
change directory to build
run pack.bat
launch.exe will appear in the build\packed directory